
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Product Page</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-turquoise: #40E0D0;
      --color-dark-turquoise: #32C6B2;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      @apply bg-[var(--color-turquoise)] text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-[var(--color-dark-turquoise)] transition duration-300;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      @apply bg-gray-100 text-[var(--color-turquoise)] border border-[var(--color-turquoise)] py-2 px-6 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-[var(--color-turquoise)] hover:text-white transition duration-300;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50">
  <header class="bg-white shadow-md py-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-turquoise)]">Product Page</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul class="flex gap-6">
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-[var(--color-turquoise)]">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-[var(--color-turquoise)]">Shop</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-[var(--color-turquoise)]">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
    <!-- Product Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6">
      <!-- Product Images -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <img src="main-image.jpg" alt="Main Product" class="w-full rounded-lg">
        <div class="flex gap-2 mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
          <img src="thumb1.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 1" class="w-20 h-20 object-cover border rounded-lg hover:shadow-md">
          <img src="thumb2.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 2" class="w-20 h-20 object-cover border rounded-lg hover:shadow-md">
          <img src="thumb3.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 3" class="w-20 h-20 object-cover border rounded-lg hover:shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product Information -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">ยกกระชับใบหน้า HIFU - ทั่วใบหน้า</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-turquoise)]">
          <span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
          <span class="text-gray-600">(4.8 - 287 reviews)</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-turquoise)] text-3xl font-bold mt-4">฿1600</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 line-through">฿3500</p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700">By: Dr. Skin</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <label for="qty" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Qty:</label>
          <input type="number" id="qty" value="1" min="1"
            class="w-20 border rounded-md p-2 mt-2 text-center shadow-sm focus:ring-[var(--color-turquoise)] focus:border-[var(--color-turquoise)]">
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6">
          <button class="btn-primary">Add to Cart</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary">Buy Now</button>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">Description</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            บริการยกกระชับผิวหน้าด้วยเทคโนโลยี HIFU ช่วยลดริ้วรอยและยกกระชับใบหน้าได้อย่างมีประสิทธิภาพ
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Recommendations Section -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">You might also like</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <!-- Recommendation Item -->
        <div class="text-center bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <img src="item1.jpg" alt="Item 1" class="w-full h-32 object-cover rounded-lg">
          <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-gray-800">The cleanser face wash</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-turquoise)] font-bold">฿18.6</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <img src="item2.jpg" alt="Item 2" class="w-full h-32 object-cover rounded-lg">
          <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-gray-800">The moisturizer</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-turquoise)] font-bold">฿25.0</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more items here -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
